(None, 'comment', 'carussell', datetime.datetime(2010, 3, 23, 21, 15, 44), 'That\'s a flawed analogy. There aren\'t artificial limitations preventing you from then publishing your own newspaper. You have no such opportunity to compete with the App Store.

Pre-emptive note: countering with a response similar to "I wasn\'t referring to the App Store; I was referring to the iPhone itself, which you are certainly free to compete with." doesn\'t just betray your analogy as incongruous. It would reveal that your analogy was helplessly broken from the start.', 1213894, [1214200], None, None, None, None)
